			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Diagram the connections among different people, groups, and organizations in your community.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Why do this">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Understanding how people or groups (i.e. actors) are connected -- by flows of resources, communication, and/or information -- can help you craft your engagement plan to best reach and include different local constituencies.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="How to do this">
			</text>	
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<icon
			width="10.0"
			height="10.0"
			id="74">
			</icon>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Meet with your core team and draw out specific relationships between community members/organizations that are involved or affected by resilience planning">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<icon
			width="10.0"
			height="10.0"
			id="74">
			</icon>
